===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|元|頁|c1=p|c2=s|ls=psc|t1=head|t2=head}}.

As {{zh-m|元|tr=-}} came to be used to mean “original”, rather than “head”, this character was formed from the original meaning of {{zh-m|元|tr=-|t=head}} + the semantic element {{zh-m|頁|tr=-}} to affirm the “head” meaning, but with the modification in meaning to “an intransigent head”; the head of a heady person.

